## Review

**Scope:** `src/config/env.ts`, `src/config/pino-config.ts`, `src/server.ts`, `tests/helpers/stripe.ts`, `tests/helpers/stripe-helpers.test.ts`, `tests/fixtures/stripe/*`, `package.json`
